Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:33.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ai, aquests corbs. Per què criden així?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:51.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ai ha tesaguri kurayami no naka de odoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a great night, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:57.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Una intriga que fa posar la pell de gallina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Enmig de la foscor, un crit vermell i una bala negra!
